::Mosquitor::

Mosquitor slams forward against the CR chamber as shots hit him in the back, making him hit his head hard. He spins around, his acid tank ruptured and spweing acid everywhere.

"Hell Beast will hear of this!" He yells as he transforms into beast mode, jumping at Hurricane with his mouthpiece ready to plunge into the other's chest (remember Celeno).
